30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:38:53.000Z","msg":"上海仲扮野<br />\n<br />\n唔嚴重停工停課做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e096b0aee9945a9b8da72ad64accc0a29c8fff7","tid":1845612,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"垃圾港府仲叫人番工"},{"pid":"7ba919ad09dce5cd1cc5f17e5bd4197e1bfe8a7d","tid":1845612,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df49103902c19588b8953229c3cc2d4b296a143","tid":1845612,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:49:16.000Z","msg":"港豬聽日最後一日假期都有人開始返去開工OT"},{"pid":"8d538c57275410985741c9a53a985fee8b28cae9","tid":1845612,"uid":177485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:49:26.000Z","msg":"港共:不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb120726afd07c5b69fba32df41713a5408249e1","tid":1845612,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:50:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3993cc2afc2bb2c95b9e869065c2b62cec20dd78","tid":1845612,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a20de71aa1cad8188f726a9519caecc179e54712","tid":1845612,"uid":162015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T09:14:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:51:30.000Z","msg":"habit - 100 years late."},{"pid":"3a3aa2e145ec6d28d03f1eeed074e9dfbe653047","tid":1845612,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:57:25.000Z","msg":"我希望大家同我一齊嗌!! 嗌到大陸都一齊嗌!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846888</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>抗疫保命<br />\n推翻政權</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}